ge_number":1,"summaries":[{"id":5093,"category":"team","content":"##Introduction\nAn attacker just needs to supply an email address to gain a valid access token for the Zomato applications. Thus any account on Zomato can be fully accessed with just the email address.\n\n#Endpoint\n`/v2/auth.json`\n\n##Impact\nCritical, without any user interaction an attacker can access any account.","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false,"attachments":[],"user":{"id":59568,"username":"chicken-tikka","name":"Vinoth Kumar","bio":"","cleared":false,"website":"https://www.zomato.com","location":"","created_at":"2016-03-07T05:24:19.957Z","url":"https://hackerone.com/chicken-tikka","anc_triager":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false,"user_type":"legacy","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/059/568/cdbb30fd8932f00a06868a737ab5bdc5c57e5f00_original.jpg/43e4513b9104ea0d68c9c096cea374ba8440dde3e027af5465c8771e8839a67c","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/059/568/cdbb30fd8932f00a06868a737ab5bdc5c57e5f00_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c","xtralarge":"https://hackerone.com/rails/active_storage/representations/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBak1rIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--c84381c8323eae0274c19f032cbf1e4a3ab12caf/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaDdCam9MY21WemFYcGxTU0lOTWpZd2VESTJNRDRHT2daRlZBPT0iLCJleHAiOm51bGwsInB1ciI6InZhcmlhdGlvbiJ9fQ==--7e37b612eb3c91a96f98ad01ca9fbe53cab870dd/9727cd5eee1e1682c09479737d4ddfc2349c5cba_xtralarge.jpg"}}},{"id":4858,"category":"researcher","content":"At some point I started focusing on the mobile app, since in my experience a mobile app has more server-side (read criticial) issues, while a webapplication has more client-side vulnerabilities. After testing the login flow for the three different options: Facebook, Google and password based, I noticed that Google login looked slightly weird in the fact that a lot of data was send besides the Google OAuth token. Thus I started stripping parameters one by one after which I noticed that only the email of a user was required to login. This request would look like:\n\n```http\nPOST /v2/auth.json?isGoogle=true HTTP/1.1\nX-API-Key: 4749b89651969b87a3kfc739o254ada2\nContent-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\nContent-Length: 21\nHost: api.zomato.com\nConnection: close\n\nemail=email@example.com\n```  \n\nThus I could login as any user on Zomato given I knew their email address.","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false,"attachments":[],"user":{"id":3237,"username":"gerben_javado","name":"Gerben Janssen van Doorn","bio":"","cleared":false,"website":"https://gerbenjavado.com/","location":"London","created_at":"2014-03-03T08:27:25.416Z","url":"https://hackerone.com/gerben_javado","anc_triager":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false,"user_type":"hacker","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/nxCLVa5sJm5BsdGjBdqzDfg8/43e4513b9104ea0d68c9c096cea374ba8440dde3e027af5465c8771e8839a67c","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/nxCLVa5sJm5BsdGjBdqzDfg8/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c","xtralarge":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/nxCLVa5sJm5BsdGjBdqzDfg8/c11036e2d3f8b05af4b5da5984ccdec6f786b763c8abceb4e68042e10dcdae85"}}}]}